org.jsfml.window

Enum Keyboard.Key

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<Keyboard.Key>
      • org.jsfml.window.Keyboard.Key
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<Keyboard.Key>
    Enclosing class:
    Keyboard

    public static enum Keyboard.Key
extends Enum<Keyboard.Key>
    Enumeration of supported keys.

    The keys in this enumeration are named after the standard QWERTY keyboard layout. Their locations and labels may vary on different keyboard layouts, even though the scan codes, and therefore their representation in this enumeration, are the same.

    There may be some non-standard keys on certain keyboards that are mapped to unknown scan codes. Those special keys will be represented by UNKNOWN.
